## Intro

No one knows how to properly edgeguard this character. 
They hold ledge, don't refresh their invincibility, and then wonder why they get clipped my Marth's upb every time. It makes me sad. Read this so I don't have to be sad anymore. 
## Flowchart

Whatever you do, don't hold ledge and challenge their upb with your upb. Marth has too many timing mix ups for it to be consistent. 

### Below Ledge

DK has one of the best Marthkillers in the game thanks to his massive lightshield. It covers every spacing of Marth upb.

<!-- marth lowsweetspotupb dk marthkiller 
https://gfycat.com/meanhardadder

