gif:https://thumbs.gfycat.com/MeanHardAdder-size_restricted.gif,https://thumbs.gfycat.com/HotThirstyCoral-size_restricted.gif

Marth's only counterplay mix up landing on stage and taking ledge, which DK can also cover. 

<!-- marth lowupbmixuptoledge dk marthkiller 
