### To Ledge

This is the hardest option for DK to cover because it's impossible to consistently react to Marth mixing up jumping to ledge going for a low upb. 

<!-- marth jumptoledge dk nocounter
https://gfycat.com/obviousyearlybluemorphobutterfly  -->
gif:https://thumbs.gfycat.com/ObviousYearlyBluemorphobutterfly-size_restricted.gif

DK's best option is to reposition with jump or to preemptively stuff Marth's Approach with upb or bair. 

