### Above Ledge

If Marth is recovering form above the ledge, DK's best bet is to shark with bair or upb. 

<!-- https://gfycat.com/beautifuldifferentaustralianfreshwatercrocodile

https://gfycat.com/elderlythirdburro -->

gif:https://thumbs.gfycat.com/ElderlyThirdBurro-size_restricted.gif,https://thumbs.gfycat.com/BeautifulDifferentAustralianfreshwatercrocodile-size_restricted.gif

The only thing Marth can do is read DK's timing with a double jump or attack, but DK always has the advantage because he can drift outside Marth's range and choose when to engage.  